!! [[0.9.4|https://crosseye.github.io/TW5-JSON_Convert/0.9.4/]]
//Released 2026-05-16//

Pass-through field picker.

* Pass-through field picker: in the Editor's Custom Fields header, a ''Pick fields…'' button opens a checkbox tree of every leaf in the source JSON; tick to add as pass-through bindings, untick to skip
* Tri-state All checkbox; Select all / Clear all bulk actions; sticky modal Apply / Cancel
* New sample: Moodle Gradebook — 6 records, ~25 fields each, including 4 "cruft" fields to demonstrate the picker
* Profile section UI: Edit always visible (disabled when no profile selected), Edit / New aligned in a right-hand column
* Profile and sample tiddlers now route into `profiles/` (via `FileSystemPaths` / `FileSystemExtensions`) so syncer-saved edits land in the conventional location
* Documentation: usage tiddler gains §7.6 + recipe §11.6; Overview, plugin readme, and README updated
* Fix: new profiles created via the editor were being tagged with the old (no-longer-watched) tag
